      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Steps to take before calculating your claim through the Job Support Scheme
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Find out what steps you need to take for JSS Open and JSS Closed before you can calculate how much you can claim. </p>

  </div>
</div>

